#include <iostream>
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	int d,y,f,c,t,i,days;
	char name[12][4]={"JAN","FEB","MAR","APR","MAY","JUN","JUL","AUG","SEP","OCT","NOV","DEC"};
	char temp[12];
	char x[4];
	cin>>t;
	c=1;
	while(t--)
	{
		int months[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
		cin>>temp;
		d=0;
		d=(d*10)+(temp[0]-'0');
		d=(d*10)+(temp[1]-'0');
		x[0]=temp[3];
		x[1]=temp[4];
		x[2]=temp[5];
		x[3]='\0';
		y=0;
		y=(y*10)+(temp[7]-'0');
		y=(y*10)+(temp[8]-'0');
		y=(y*10)+(temp[9]-'0');
		y=(y*10)+(temp[10]-'0');
		f=0;
		if(y%400==0||(y%4==0&&y%100!=0))
			f=1;
		if(f==1)
			months[1]=29;
		i=0;
		days=0;
		while(strcmp(name[i],x)!=0)
		{
			days=days+months[i];
			i++;
		}
		days=days+d;
		if(days<=300)
		{
			cout<<"Case "<<c++<<": "<<days<<" Hundreds\n";
			continue;
		}
		else if(days<=360)
		{
			days=days-300;
			cout<<"Case "<<c++<<": "<<days<<" Tens\n";
			continue;
		}
		else
		{
			days=days-360;
			cout<<"Case "<<c++<<": "<<days<<" Ones\n";
		}
	}
	return 0;
}
